Usage: focus [-i|--input INPUT-FILE] [-o|--output OUTPUT-FILE] [--no-color] 
             [--full] COMMAND

  Focus - cli utility for hacking and slashing data

Available options:
  -i,--input INPUT-FILE    File to use for input. Defaults to stdin if
                           unspecified
  -o,--output OUTPUT-FILE  File to use for output. Defaults to stdout if
                           unspecified
  --no-color               Disable colored output
  --full                   Process the entire input at once instead of
                           line-by-line
  -h,--help                Show this help text

Available commands:
  view                     View the focus
  modify                   Modify the focused field
  set                      Set the focus
